After failing twice to complete Bright's 24-hour challenge, I finally manage to make one in 2 hours and he downvotes it. Such is life, I guess.

The image has definitely appeared on the wiki before, in Document 8668206 Dg, and if someone else made a main-list article for it before me they should have removed it from that list. I've always wanted to write an article for one of the images on that list, and I finally had a decent idea for one, so I decided to go for it.

Thanks for all the feedback. I've gone back through and fixed some of the errors that people have pointed out, and explained the lack of amnesiac use.

And, of course, mad props to Gears for compiling the images document I found the original image in, and to Raven Mackenzie for adding the tags to this article after I forgot to.







